{{Infobox software | name = Zoho Survey | title = | logo = Zoho Survey.png | logo size = 220px | screenshot = <!-- Image name is enough --> | developer = [[Zoho Corporation]] | released = {{Start date and age|2013|07|01|df=yes}} | discontinued = | latest release version = | latest release date = <!-- {{Start date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|df=yes/no}} --> | latest preview version = | latest preview date = <!-- {{Start date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|df=yes/no}} --> | status = | programming language = | operating system = [[Cross-platform]] (web-based application) | platform = | size = | language = | language count = 32 | language footnote = | genre = [[Software as a Service]] | license = | alexa = 626 | website = {{URL|https://www.zoho.com/survey}} }}
'''Zoho Survey''' is an [[Survey data collection#Online surveys|online survey]] creation tool, launched on July 1, 2013.<ref>{{cite news|title=Zoho Launches Mobile-Ready Survey Tool To Extend Online Business Platform|url=https://techcrunch.com/2013/07/01/zoho-launches-mobile-ready-survey-tool-to-extend-online-business-platform|accessdate=February 4, 2015|newspaper=TechCrunch|date=July 1, 2013|author=}}</ref> It is part of a larger suite of cloud-based ("[[software as a service]]") applications, the [[Zoho Office Suite]].
Zoho Survey provides its users with unlimited free and [[customizable]] surveys, which may be launched from various [[Gadget|devices]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Zoho Launches Zoho Survey|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20130701006349/en/Zoho-Launches-Zoho-Survey|accessdate=February 4, 2015|newspaper=Business Insider|date=July 1, 2013|author=}}</ref> It also provides its individual and [[enterprise resource planning|enterprise]] level users with advanced features like [[multilingual]] support, branded surveys, advanced [[Data reporting|reporting]], and the ability to share, review and [[collaborate]] on surveys.
== Features == Zoho Survey primary feature is its ability to create an unlimited number of customized surveys.
The features of Zoho Survey is as follows:
=== Survey Design === * [[iOS]] Application <ref>{{cite news|title=Zoho Debuts Survey Building Tool|url=http://www.cmswire.com/cms/customer-experience/zoho-debuts-survey-building-tool-021583.php|accessdate=February 4, 2015|newspaper=CMS Wire|date=July 1, 2013|author=Anthony Myers}}</ref> * Question and Page [[Mathematical logic|Logic]] * Auto Fill * Piping * [[Multilingual]] and [[Brand management|Branded]] Surveys * [[Notification system|Email notifications]] * [[Collaboration]] in Surveys * Export/Print Survey
=== Response Collection === * Share surveys on [[Social media]] * [[HTML element#embed|Embed Surveys]] * [[QR code]] * Offline Survey * Protection against automated responses * Optimized for [[Mobile devices]]
=== Analytics === * Export [[reports]] in [[pdf]] and [[Microsoft Excel|excel]] formats * Download [[charts]] * Customize reports * [[Contingency table|Cross tab reports]] * [[Trend Analysis|Trend reports]] * Filter Responses
== Integrations == Zoho Survey comes with the ability to integrate with [[Zoho Office Suite#Zoho CRM|Zoho CRM]], Zoho Campaigns, [[Facebook]], [[MailChimp]], [[Google Docs|Google Spreadsheet]], and [[Google Apps Marketplace]].
